raw_body: JOE (NAGE) VICTORIA – It is with profound sadness that we announce the death of JOE (NAGE) VICTORIA. Beloved husband of Swarna (deceased) and son Luckshan (deceased),​ loving brother of Selve,​ Mirani,​ late Raj,​ Wije,​ Mahe and Agnes. Remains lie at Western Florists Funeral Parlour,​ Negombo on 22nd July from 8.30 a.m. to 3.30 p.m. Burial on the 22nd July at Raddoluwa Cemetery at 4.30 p.m.044987
